Scholarships and Financial Aid with Qadri International
Financial aid and scholarships are available for eligible students studying in Cyprus. Qadri International can provide information on the various scholarships and financial aid options available, as well as assist you in applying for them. Don't let finances be a barrier to your education –  study in Cyprus with Qadri International and unlock your future!

Student Life in Cyprus
Life as a student in Cyprus is vibrant and exciting. You'll have the opportunity to meet students from all over the world, participate in a variety of clubs and activities, and explore the country's rich cultural heritage. Whether you're hiking in the mountains, swimming in the sea, or exploring the local markets, you'll find that there is never a dull moment in Cyprus.

